    "description": "Dear Kosisochukwu,\n\nI hope this mail meets you well.\n\nIn view of your interest for an internship position within our firm , you have been scheduled for an interview.\n\nDate – Monday, April 28th, 2025.\n\nTime – 2:00pm – 2:30pm\n\nYou are required to prepare a PowerPoint Presentation to present on: “Why you want to join your preferred service line (Assurance, Consulting, SAT, or TAX) in the firm and why you think you are the best candidate to be considered.”\n\nKindly accept this calendar invite and see meeting link below.\n\nPlease see useful tips for the virtual interview:\n\n  *   be advised to use a laptop for the best experience and have multiple internet providers as back-up.\n  *   be advised to join the meeting at least 5 minutes to the time for the interview, you will be granted access once the meeting is about to commence\n  *   ensure your device (laptop/tab/mobile phone) is multimedia (video and audio) enabled.\n  *   ensure you stay in a properly lit space and away from noisy environment.\n  *   ensure you are dressed formally and appropriately, and your hair is neatly done\nThis list is not exhaustible as all other interview guidelines are applicable.\n________________________________________________________________________________\nMicrosoft Teams Need help?<https://aka.ms/JoinTeamsMeeting?omkt=en-US>\nJoin the meeting now<https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_OGUzZWMwMjMtMzc1MC00MmYwLWFhMDctODYzYmZlNDhhMjk1%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%225b973f99-77df-4beb-b27d-aa0c70b8482c%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%222fe08e95-e147-4109-8045-3e41c8c1feb1%22%7d>\nMeeting ID: 236 954 257 347 2\nPasscode: wD9xv7wj\n________________________________\nJoin on a video conferencing device\nTenant key: 971828598@t.plcm.vc\nVideo ID: 118 978 210 20\nMore info<https://dialin.plcm.vc/teams/?key=971828598&conf=11897821020>\nFor organizers: Meeting options<https://teams.microsoft.com/meetingOptions/?organizerId=2fe08e95-e147-4109-8045-3e41