    "description": "Topic: Lets Build a $10k/Month AI Software in 40 Minutes and Get Customers FULL DEMO\nDescription: How to Build, Launch & Get Paying Customers for Your Own AI Software (Live Demo)\nIn this free live workshop, Jonathan Montoya and Stefan Ciancio will build an entire software business from complete scratch in under 60 minutes. \n\nThis is not a slideshow. You will watch the entire process happen live on screen.\n\nHere's what you'll see:\nStep 1: We'll use AI to find a profitable software idea backed by real market data. You'll see the exact process for identifying ideas with proven demand, high search volume, and weak competition so you know people will actually pay for it before you build anything.\n\nStep 2: We'll validate the idea live using a 10-point scoring system that analyzes competitors, search demand, market size, financial projections, and risk assessment. You'll see exactly how to know if an idea is worth building or if you should move on.\n\nStep 3: We'll build the entire software live using AI. No coding. No developers. Just copy and paste prompts into a tool called Lovable that builds the landing page, dashboard, user authentication, payment processing, and every feature. You'll watch it get built in real time.\n\nStep 4: This is the part nobody else shows you. We'll generate a complete 30-day marketing plan to get paying customers. Daily content scripts, YouTube video topics and full scripts, short-form video scripts, and a proven organic posting strategy that has generated over 150 million views. All customized to the specific software we just built.\n\nThis framework is backed by $18 million in combined online sales between the two hosts. \n\nonathan is a former electrical engineer who has built 5 AI software products with thousands of paying users without writing a single line of code. Stefan is the founder of WebinarKit with over 20,000 users and $8 million in career online sales.\n\nTheir community of over 2,000 AI software builders is already using this system to launch real products and get real customers in industries ranging from healthcare to real estate\n\nJoin from PC, Mac, iPad, or Android:\nhttps://us02web.zoom.us/w/82603419673?tk=2DZPzL-v113Bl_NuEKipoZAcO08ULTd2rLDabDYyInA.DQkAAAATO4woGRZDWXNSTmFoSFRGR2NRMVBuaGdIbGNBAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA&pwd=FLaemHbSqwAqLa6tR4M7wt4N6R6DGs.1&uuid=WN_F1WANYkTSz-lvewq49l1UQ\nPasscode:509689\n\nPhone one-tap:\n+13462487799,,82603419673#,,,,*509689# US (Houston)\n+13602095623,,82603419673#,,,,*509689# US\n\nJoin via audio:\n+1 346 248 7799 US (Houston)\n+1 360 209 5623 US\n+1 386 347 5053 US\n+1 507 473 4847 US\n+1 564 217 2000 US\n+1 646 931 3860 US\n+1 669 444 9171 US\n+1 669 900 6833 US (San Jose)\n+1 689 278 1000 US\n+1 719 359 4580 US\n+1 929 205 6099 US (New York)\n+1 253 205 0468 US\n+1 253 215 8782 US (Tacoma)\n+1 301 715 8592 US (Washington DC)\n+1 305 224 1968 US\n+1 309 205 3325 US\n+1 312 626 6799 US (Chicago)\nWebinar ID: 826 0341 9673\nPasscode: 509689\nInternational numbers available: https://us02web.zoom.us/u/kdkYcNnBgy\n\n\n",
